reviewText:
Well, now I have all Hell Girl episodes on DVD and I could not be happier with the item therefore I am happy... honestly
though I am happy with the transaction thanks.
All good.  Not English dubbed but does have subtitles!  Glad I bought this.  Liked the story and hope for another season!
same old story of demons on earth
I was so very happy to receive the third and final set of the Hell Girl series.  The dvd's were in great condition, they played well, and I have really enjoyed each episode.
The anime is great, loved it so much. The case was in plastic wrap and was in new condition. Had no problems and would recommend this to anyone. :)
This is a great show. My only problem is that it isn't dubbed in english like the first season. I don't mind reading subs. But I do prefer dubs to subs.
I am in love with this series, and my boyfriend bough me the first season collection, so I treated myself to this one.
